### 🎨 Theme
- Black-and-white minimalist trading aesthetic.
- Primary accent: gradient teal → purple.
- Use CSS variables (`--gradient-primary`, `--radius-lg`, etc.) from `:root`.

### ✨ Components
- Monetary displays: `$USD` primary line + SOL equivalent in muted text.
- Use shadcn/ui primitives for consistent accessibility and focus states.
- Apply glass-morphism and subtle glow to cards and modals.
- Motion: Framer-Motion fade/slide; 150–300 ms transitions.

### 📐 Typography
- Headings: IBM Plex Sans Bold
- Data text: JetBrains Mono
- Secondary text: muted gray (oklch(0.6 0 0))